headline: Erin Mills,  Mark Haslinger Jr.
abstract: The couple met in 2013 through Match.com, the online dating service, and had their first date in New York.
lead_paragraph: Erin Patricia Mills and Mark Peter Haslinger Jr. were married Dec. 31 at St. Alphonsus Roman Catholic Church in Hopewell, N.J. Msgr. Luke M. Sweeney, a cousin of the bride, performed the ceremony.
